{
  "stem": "27507.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she was then a director of the hospital in Soviet-occupied part of Poland, in a place called [POLISH], and-- in a small town in East Poland.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she must have taken the Soviet nationality, because she never went-- she was never deported.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was just the director of this hospital in [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she was sending us packs, food packages to the ghetto, which were something which was terribly important, because we-- it was fantastic that there were still packages of-- it was honey and there was some tins.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there was maybe butter I think she was sending.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they were still arriving, those packets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But after the war started with the Russians, briefly after, the packages--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--stopped coming and letters from Mania stopped coming and we lost contact with her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, we never knew anything what happened to her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, she was there, as most of the Jewish population in those areas, together with her husband, they were all shot together, the whole Jewish population of the town was-- we found about it after the war-- was gathered together and they were just shot, probably in early stages of the war, some time in summer 1941.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- but we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just-- there was no contact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nothing happening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but in '42, the things started happening which were strange.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were suddenly-- they started in ghetto, the Germans started-- there were all kinds of signs which meant that things were not--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're changing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were those films which I said-- I spoke about before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were filming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were coming and they were closing certain area.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
